data.description:
Recently updated (between 2017-2023) 3/2.5 single family lakefront pool home in a manned gated community in the heart of a picturesque neighborhood in Central Boca Raton! Nestled amidst lush greenery and offering an idyllic blend of elegance and comfort, this charming abode is a must-see for discerning buyers.As you step through the inviting front door, you'll be greeted by an open-concept living space adorned with abundant natural light, creating a warm and inviting ambiance. The spacious living room is perfect for family gatherings, while the huge modern kitchen boasts custom built cabinets, wide island great for entertaining, coffee bar, stainless steel appliances including two ovens, sinks, dishwashers, microwaves, hot and main water sources, amazing space for culinary enthusiast. A serene master bedroom retreat awaits on the main floor, complete with a luxurious en-suite bathroom and ample closet space. Upstairs, discover generously sized bedrooms with large windows that frame breathtaking views of the surrounding landscape.

Step outside to your private oasis, where a beautifully lighted landscaped backyard beckons for relaxation and entertaining overlooking the lake. Imagine hosting summer barbecues with your built-in with a 7 burner KitchenAid grill on the patio, gathering around at the stone bar or simply unwinding under the stars in your tranquil garden.

This home is not just a place to live but a lifestyle to savor. Don't miss the chance to make it yours; schedule a viewing today and start living the dream!
